ki/List_of_Portuguese_supercentenarians" title="List of Portuguese supercentenarians">Portuguese</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/List_of_Spanish_supercentenarians" title="List of Spanish supercentenarians">Spanish</a></span>)</div>
